  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0df2ddcceb2389b4d864a64d8b7d2cf4, type: 3}
  m_Name: SO_Dialogue_StoreRoomDishesAfterCobwebs
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  background: {fileID: 0}
  lines:
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "H\u1EBFt d\u1ECDn nh\u00E0 kho, c\u00F2n \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\u1ED1ng b\u00E1t \u0111\u0169a n\u1EEFa... haizz."
    englishText: The storage room is done, and now there is that pile of dishes too... sigh.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Silly
    englishSpeakerName: Silly
    text: "B\u00E1t \u0111\u0169a n\u1EEFa \u00E0... n\u1EBFu m\u00ECnh r\u1EEDa xong, c\u1EADu \u1EA5y s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y m\u00ECnh c\u00F3 \u00EDch."
    englishText: Dishes too... if I wash them, he will see that I am useful.
    portrait: {fileID: 6468568510307345621, guid: 0c05e137063d43e429af4b01ffae35ac, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Silly
    englishSpeakerName: Silly
    text: "L\u1EA7n n\u00E0y ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn V\u0169 s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EC3 \u00FD."
    englishText: This time, Vu will definitely notice.
    portrait: {fileID: 6468568510307345621, guid: 0c05e137063d43e429af4b01ffae35ac, type: 3}
